"v.积聚 【英】 v. 积聚(collect together; to accumulate) 【记】 a+mass(一团)→变成 一团→积聚 【同】 同根词：massive(巨 大的); massacre(大屠杀) v. 积聚(尤指财富) = garner = hive = stockpile 【例】During each war the monopoly capitalists amassed fabulous wealth 每次战争垄断资本家们都大发横财. 【记】mass大块, 堆, 一团－变成大块－积聚 【参】massive(adj 巨大的); massacre(n /v 大屠杀) 【记】a + mass 块，大量，聚集 amass (v.)  late 15c., ""to heap up for oneself,"" from Old French amasser, from à ""to"" (see ad-) + masser (see mass (n.1)). Related: Amassed; amassing."
